    "body": "You can call `.sort_values` on the `MultiIndex` itself and pass to `reindex`.\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndf.reindex(index=df.index.sort_values())\r\nOut[156]: \r\nEmpty DataFrame\r\nColumns: []\r\nIndex: [(0.5, b), (0.8, a)]\r\n```"
